SVG is a module for creating Scalable Vector Graphics in Perl 6. Copyright
2009, the SVG contributors (as listed in AUTHORS).

The specification outlining SVG can be found here: <http://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/>

== Getting SVG up and running

=== ...with proto

 $ git clone git://github.com/masak/proto.git  # (1) download proto installer
 $ cd proto
 $ ./proto install svg                         # (2) use it to install SVG
 $ cd projects/svg
 $ perl6 svg-example                           # (3) ...and you're off!

=== ...without proto

TBW. :)

